  text_en: 'The concept from which this project originates states, as we mention one line above, the intention of turning this skin wellness and beauty center into a beacon of its kind. For that reason, the façade is presented as a grand gateway to a better state for all its future users, taking them along a self-contained luxury interior, loaded with a warm and welcoming atmosphere.',
